# NZ English Spelling

## Rule

**Use NZ English (British-style) spelling for all user-facing copy.**

Applies to:
- UI text (labels, buttons, headings, descriptions)
- Marketing and landing copy
- Error messages and toast text
- Documentation written in this repo
- Email and notification copy
- Strings in code that are shown to users

